                                                            <p style="text-align: left;">शिवगर्जना कार्यक्रमातील एक क्षण.सांगली</p>
                                                            <p style="text-align: left;">अभिनेते खा. डॉ अमोल कोल्हे यांनी शिवाश्रम ला दिलेल्या शुभेच्छा</p>
                                                            <p style="text-align: center;">
                                                            <div style="width: 640px;" class="wp-video">
                                                               <video class="wp-video-shortcode" id="video-96-2" width="640" height="352" preload="metadata" controls="controls">
                                                                  <source type="video/mp4" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/WhatsApp-Video-2021-02-12-at-15.42.59.mp4?_=2" />
                                                                  <a href="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/WhatsApp-Video-2021-02-12-at-15.42.59.mp4">https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/WhatsApp-Video-2021-02-12-at-15.42.59.mp4</a>
                                                               </video>
                                                            </div>
                                                            </p>
                                                            <p style="text-align: left;">राज्यमंत्री बच्चुभाऊ कडू यांनी शिवाश्रम ला दिलेल्या शुभेच्छा,</p>
                                                            <p style="text-align: center;"> 
                                                            <div style="width: 640px;" class="wp-video">
                                                               <video class="wp-video-shortcode" id="video-96-3" width="640" height="352" preload="metadata" controls="controls">
                                                                  <source type="video/mp4" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/WhatsApp-Video-2021-02-12-at-15.44.51.mp4?_=3" />
                                                                  <a href="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/WhatsApp-Video-2021-02-12-at-15.44.51.mp4">https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/WhatsApp-Video-2021-02-12-at-15.44.51.mp4</a>
                                                               </video>
                                                            </div>
                                                            </p>
                                                            <p style="text-align: center;">शिवसेनाप्रमुख बाळासाहेब ठाकरे यांची शेवटची  वी. भेट १३ मार्च २०१२. प्रत्येक भेट एक तासाची राहिली मात्र ५० वी. भेट झालीच नाही,शिवसेनाप्रमुखांची दुसरी भेट २२ मार्च १९९५ शिवसेना भवन मुंबई ,१९९५ साली. हिंदुह्रदयसम्राट या पोवाड्याची कॅसेट महाराष्ट्रामध्ये अत्यंत लोकप्रिय झाल्याने व्हीनस कॅसेट कंपनीने प्लॅटिनम डिस्क देऊन शिवसेनाप्रमुखांच्या हस्ते सन्मान केला.</p>
                                                            <p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-2876" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/23-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="317" height="211" srcset="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/23-300x200.jpg 300w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/23-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/23-768x512.jpg 768w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/23-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/23-600x400.jpg 600w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/23.jpg 1800w" sizes="(max-width: 317px) 100vw, 317px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2879" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/14159769_1067796456666854_1665649874_n-300x219.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="219" srcset="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/14159769_1067796456666854_1665649874_n-300x219.jpg 300w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/14159769_1067796456666854_1665649874_n-600x437.jpg 600w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/14159769_1067796456666854_1665649874_n.jpg 708w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-2936" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/photo08.jpg" alt="" width="308" height="205" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2898" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20140903-WA0065-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" srcset="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20140903-WA0065-300x200.jpg 300w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20140903-WA0065-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20140903-WA0065-768x512.jpg 768w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20140903-WA0065-600x400.jpg 600w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20140903-WA0065.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2888" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/balasaheb-thakare-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" srcset="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/balasaheb-thakare-300x200.jpg 300w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/balasaheb-thakare-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/balasaheb-thakare-768x512.jpg 768w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/balasaheb-thakare-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/balasaheb-thakare-600x400.jpg 600w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/balasaheb-thakare.jpg 1800w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-2897" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/images.jpg" alt="" width="302" height="201" /></p>
                                                            <p>इयत्ता चौथी पासुन शिवशाहीर बाबासाहेब पुरंदरे यांचे सानिध्य मिळाले</p>
                                                            <p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-2893" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/DSC_3279-300x199.jpg" alt="" width="338" height="224" srcset="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/DSC_3279-300x199.jpg 300w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/DSC_3279-1024x679.jpg 1024w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/DSC_3279-768x509.jpg 768w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/DSC_3279-1536x1019.jpg 1536w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/DSC_3279-2048x1358.jpg 2048w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/DSC_3279-600x398.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 338px) 100vw, 338px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2887" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/babasaheb-purandare-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/babasaheb-purandare-300x225.jpg 300w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/babasaheb-purandare-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/babasaheb-purandare-768x576.jpg 768w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/babasaheb-purandare-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/babasaheb-purandare-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/babasaheb-purandare-600x450.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
                                                            <p>३० जानेवारी १९८७ रोजी पद्मश्री अण्णा हजारे यांच्या हस्ते बालशाहीर पुरस्कार मिळाला. त्यानंतर अनेकदा अण्णांचे सानिध्य लाभत आहे.</p>
                                                            <p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-2924" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20200315-WA0088-300x169.jpg" alt="" width="357" height="201" srcset="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20200315-WA0088-300x169.jpg 300w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20200315-WA0088-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20200315-WA0088-768x432.jpg 768w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20200315-WA0088-600x338.jpg 600w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20200315-WA0088.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 357px) 100vw, 357px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2901" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20140913-WA0073-300x199.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="199" srcset="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20140913-WA0073-300x199.jpg 300w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20140913-WA0073-1024x678.jpg 1024w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20140913-WA0073-768x509.jpg 768w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20140913-WA0073-600x398.jpg 600w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/IMG-20140913-WA0073.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
                                                            <p>माननीय छत्रपती खासदार उदयनराजे भोसले यांच्या भेटीला गेल्यावर प्रत्येक वेळी गाडीपर्यंत सोडवायला येतात खूप मोठ्या मनाचे व्यक्तीमत्व</p>
