                                                            <p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2882" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/21032878_1454239984690243_6781608023465292094_n-300x226.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="226" srcset="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/21032878_1454239984690243_6781608023465292094_n-300x226.jpg 300w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/21032878_1454239984690243_6781608023465292094_n-600x453.jpg 600w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/21032878_1454239984690243_6781608023465292094_n.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-2883" src="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/21078468_1454240464690195_5994807616179691661_n-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" srcset="https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/21078468_1454240464690195_5994807616179691661_n-300x225.jpg 300w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/21078468_1454240464690195_5994807616179691661_n-600x450.jpg 600w, https://drvijaytanpure.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/21078468_1454240464690195_5994807616179691661_n.jpg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>
                                                            <p>अभिनेते दादा कोंडके यांच्या समवेत बारागाव नांदूर येथे (१९८७) ,डॉ. प्रकाश बाबा आमटे डॉ. मंदाकिनी आमटे यांचे हस्ते यशाचा नवा मंत्र शिवतंत्र या सीडीचे प्रकाशनाच्या वेळी पुणे येथे</p>
